'''Imbraani''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Qiilura/Legends|Qiilura]].

After the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] took over Imbraani, they stationed both a research facility and a villa for the [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] [[Lik Ankkit]] there. [[Ghez Hokan]] used the Neimoidian's villa to store [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]]. The research facility was eventually infiltrated by [[Omega Squad]]. Imbraani and Qiilura would eventually be abandoned by the [[Human/Legends|Human]] colonists as the need for the [[Gurlanin]]s was in more demand by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] than Human colonization of Qiilura. A group of farmers who stayed behind tried to fight to keep their homes but were eventually removed after suffering a few casualties.

